General.Name: Fortnox AB
General.Description: Fortnox AB (publ) operates a cloud-based business platform for financial administration for small businesses, accounting firms, associations, and schools. It offers industry solutions for bookkeeping, billing, quotation and order, salary, stock, time reporting, and receipt and travel. It also offers invoicing software and payroll program. Fortnox AB (publ) was incorporated in 1993 and is headquartered in Växjö, Sweden.
